@startuml
title
<size:16><b>UC-10: Track Order - Activity Diagram</b></size>
end title

|Buyer|
start

:Navigate to 'My Orders' from dashboard;

|System|
:Display list of all orders placed by Buyer with status indicators;

|Buyer|
:Select an order to view details;

|System|
:Display Order ID, Date Placed, Items, Seller, Total, Current Status,
 and Status History timeline (Confirmed → Packed → Shipped → Delivered);

|Seller|
:Update order status from dashboard (Packed or Shipped);

|System|
:Send email notification to Buyer at each status change;

if (Order status not updated within 3 business days of confirmation?) then (yes)
  :Send automated reminder to Seller;
  note right: Alternative Flow 1
else (no)
endif

|Buyer|
:Mark order as 'Received' upon delivery;

stop
@enduml